accountSetup.masterkeyFileTemplate:
Concrnt Master Key
This file is used to recover your Concrnt account.
Store this file in a safe place.

CCID: {{ccid}}
Master Key: {{mnemonic}}
Registered server: {{domain}}

If you lose your master key, you may not be able to recover your account.
If someone else learns this information, your account may be taken over.

id.backupFileContent:
Concrnt Web login information
This file is a backup of your Concrnt Web login information.
Keep this file in a safe place.

CCID: {{ccid}}
Master private key: {{privateKey}}
Registered server at backup: {{server}}

If you lose your private key, you may not be able to recover your account.
If anyone else learns this information, your account could be taken over.

